
The Airline Game
================

UI: two columns
-Messages stream by on the left
-Menus of commands / control panels appear on the right
-Single-key commands
-Spacebar to pause/unpause

Runtime: one process per airport, plus one for planes in the air, and the main (UI)
process

Main menu: show each save file as a company name and date (maybe some other info too)
-Plus a New Game option

Libraries and modules to use:
-Async
-Unix.create_process
-Curses

